{"questionId":"12932","questionHtml":"<p>Hence or otherwise find the value of <em>θ</em> for which&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{Re}}\\left( {\\frac{z}{{z - 2a}}} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>Re</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>if&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{Re}}\\left( {\\frac{z}{{z - 2a}}} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>Re</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span> then&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2\\theta&nbsp; - \\pi&nbsp; = \\frac{{n\\pi }}{2}\">\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>π</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>n</mi>\n      <mi>π</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>, (<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span> odd)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" - \\pi&nbsp; < 2\\theta&nbsp; - \\pi&nbsp; < 0 \\Rightarrow n =&nbsp; - 1\">\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>π</mi>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>π</mi>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2\\theta&nbsp; - \\pi&nbsp; =&nbsp; - \\frac{\\pi }{2}\">\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>π</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>π</mi>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\theta&nbsp; = \\frac{\\pi }{4}\">\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>π</mi>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD&nbsp;2</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{a + b{\\text{i}}}}{{ - a + b{\\text{i}}}} = \\frac{{{b^2} - {a^2} - 2ab{\\text{i}}}}{{{a^2} + {b^2}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>i</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>i</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>b</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>i</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>b</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{Re}}\\left( {\\frac{z}{{z - 2a}}} \\right) = 0 \\Rightarrow {b^2} - {a^2} = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>Re</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b = a\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\theta&nbsp; = \\frac{\\pi }{4}\">\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>π</mi>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Accept any equivalent, <em>eg&nbsp;</em><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\theta&nbsp; =&nbsp; - \\frac{{7\\pi }}{4}\">\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>7</mn>\n      <mi>π</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12932","referenceCode":"19M.2.AHL.TZ1.H_6c","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Hence or otherwise find the value of θ for which Re ( z z − 2 a ) = 0 .","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.13—Polar and Euler form"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}